(or at least toxic nationalism).

77
00:06:19.530 --> 00:06:24.310
As the story goes on there are further examples
of the way the citizens of No.6 take the city’s

78
00:06:24.310 --> 00:06:29.250
protections for granted, further reinforcing
the ideas established in the opening sequence.

79
00:06:29.250 --> 00:06:34.010
However, where No.6 stands out from many of
its contemporaries is the dedication to showing

80
00:06:34.010 --> 00:06:38.420
how the population itself has a passive role
in its own persecution.

81
00:06:38.420 --> 00:06:44.710
