115
00:08:42.919 --> 00:08:45.280
Intellect with loyalty is a good thing.

116
00:08:45.280 --> 00:08:47.620
Intellect with critical thinking is a liability.

117
00:08:47.620 --> 00:08:51.190
It’s why the modern academic curriculum
— especially in America — promotes STEM

118
